(according to 
<bibRefCitation id="200160A1C1317E4DFD7D142AFCC89A05" author="Lauck, D. R." box="[652,783,522,545]" pageId="24" pageNumber="25" pagination="34 - 81" refId="ref58101" refString="Lauck, D. R. (1962) A monograph of the genus Belostoma (Hemiptera) Part I. Introduction to B. dentatum and subspinosum groups. Bulletin of the Chicago Academy of Sciences, 11 (3), 34 - 81." type="journal article" year="1962">Lauck 1962</bibRefCitation>
